locality: Stawelklip (Piketberg). Dry Proteoid Fynbos (Campbell 1985); Vegetation cover 85%; Mature vegetation, at least 8 years old. Overstorey (Protea) c. 3 m; understorey c. 1 m.
Table Mountain, Blind Gully N-slope on rocks directly adjacent to stream.
Karbonkelberg. S slope ridge facing W Table Mountain Sandstone.
